## Required Sections In Every SKILL.md

Every agents scaffold skill should follow the common operational structure:

1. `Overview`
2. `This Skill Can Do`
3. `This Skill Must Not Claim`
4. `Route Adjacent Work`
5. `Read First`
6. `Inputs This Skill Needs`
7. `Required Decisions`
8. `Build Rules`
9. `Review Rules`
10. `Validation Checklist`
11. `This Skill Must Stop And Escalate When`

## Cleanup Goals

- keep `AGENTS.md` as the global contract and orchestrator rule set
- keep `project_builder` thin
- move all detailed `agent_scaffold/` file semantics into `maintenance/local_journal`
- keep domain skills free of project-state maintenance details

